HEADWORD: Unpoised
<hw>Un*poised"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Not
poised or balanced.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not poised or weighed; hence, regardless of
consequences; unhesitating.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Marston.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unpoison</ent>⟦br⟧
